        <h2 id="1st" class="food">Recipe #1 - Quesedilla</h2>
        
        <ul>
            <li>Time: 3-5 minutes</li>
            <li>Serves: 1 person</li>
        </ul>
        
       <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Ingridients</th>
                    <th>Quantity</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>Pita</td>
                    <td>2 pcs.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Packed Sandwhich Cheese</td>
                    <td>2 pcs.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Butter</td>
                    <td>1 tsp.</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        
        <h3><em>-- Instructions:</em></h3>
        
        <p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Turn the pan on and pre-heat.
</p>
 <p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Add butter and let it melt.
</p>
 <p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Add one piece of pita then add cheese on top and cover with 2nd layer of pita.
</p>
 <p><strong>Step 4:</strong> Turn the heated pita around after 25 seconds each side 2 times.
</p>

        <h2 id="2nd" class="food">Recipe #2 - French Toast</h2>
        
         <ul>
            <li>Time: 8-10 minutes</li>
            <li>Serves: 1 person</li>
        </ul>
        
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Ingridients</th>
                    <th>Quantity</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>Brown Bread</td>
                    <td>2 pcs.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Packed Sandwhich Cheese</td>
                    <td>2 pcs.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Butter</td>
                    <td>2 tsp.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Beated Egg</td>
                    <td>3 pcs.</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        
        <h3><em>-- Instructions:</em></h3>
        
        <p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Preheat pan and add butter.
</p>
<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Add beated egg in bowl and soak brown bread until fully soaked.
</p>
<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Add cheese in between two bread.
</p>
<p><strong>Step 4:</strong> Add bread in pan and turn fried bread around every 1 minute two times.
</p>
        
        <h2 id="3rd" class="food">Recipe #3 - Easy Salad</h2>
        
        <ul>
            <li>Time: 10-15 minutes</li>
            <li>Serves: 1-2 people</li>
        </ul>
        
       <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Ingridients</th>
                    <th>Quantity</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>Olive Oil</td>
                    <td>2 pcs.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Chopped Lettuce</td>
                    <td>2 cups</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Corn</td>
                    <td>3/4 cup</td>
                </tr>
                 <tr>
                    <td>Red Diced Onion</td>
                    <td>1/4 cup</td>
                </tr>
                 <tr>
                    <td>Shredded Cheddar Cheese</td>
                    <td>1/2 cup</td>
                </tr>
                 <tr>
                    <td>Ranch Dressing</td>
                    <td>1/4 cup</td>
                </tr>
                 <tr>
                    <td>Diced Tomato</td>
                    <td>1 pc.</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        
        <h3><em>-- Instructions:</em></h3>
        
      <p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Add chopped lettuce, corn, diced onion, cheese, and tomato in bowl. Stir & mix.
</p>
<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Add Olive oil. Stir & mix.
</p>
<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Add Ranch Dressing. Stir & mix.
</p>

